The paper presents a real-time algorithm for emotion-aware navigation of a robot among pedestrians, which involves estimating emotional behaviors of pedestrians from their faces and trajectories using Bayesian-inference, CNN-based learning, and the PAD model from psychology. This suggests that the paper could belong to the Robotics (cs.RO), Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition (cs.CV), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Human-Computer Interaction (cs.HC), or Machine Learning (cs.LG) sub-categories.
